</p>

<p class="bibl">Houfe, Simon. "Barnard, Fred." <span class="book">The Dictionary of 19th Century British Book Illustrators</span>. Woodbridge, Suffolk: The Antique Collerctors'
Club, 1978, revised 1996. </p>

